<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <% include partials/header %>
    <section class="intro-api container text-center ">
      <div class="row">
        <p class="intro_title">SHOES SALES API</p>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <p class="description">Api que retorna la informacion de zapatos, devolviendo informacion como nombre precio stock
        </p>
      </div>

    </section>

    <section class="try container text-start">
      <div class="row">
        <p class="try-it__text">
          Try It!!
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="container-try">
            <p class="link-text"  >http://localhost:3000/api/</p>
            <input id = "input-query" class ="" value = "items" type="text" placeholder="items">
            <button class ="btn" id="btn-request">Request</button>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </section>

    <section class="container show-response">
      <p id="response-text"class="response-text">
        [
        <% arrItems.forEach(function(item){ %> 
          
          <br>{<br>
            "idItem":  <%= item.idItem %>, <br>
            "nombre": <%= item.nombre %>, <br>
            "descripcion": <%= item.descripcion %>,<br>
            "precio": <%= item.precio %>,<br>
            "stock": <%= item.precio %>,<br>
            "category": <%= item.category %>,<br>
            "urlImg": <%= item.urlImg %>,<br>
          }<br>
         
         
        <% }); %>  
        ]
      </p>
    </section>

    <div class="container acordion-container">
      <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
            <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
              get items/:category
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <strong>Para este get se debe agregar una categoria conocida </strong> 
              se debe escribir en el input items/Most Exclusive y retornara unalistacon la informacion de los items que pertenezcan a esa categoria en formato json
              las categorias que existen son 1.Most Exclusive 2. Jordan 3. Jeezy 4. Air Force
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
              get items/item/:id
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <strong>Para este Get necesitamos pasarle un id que exista de lo contrario retorna vacio.</strong>
              se debe escribir en el input items/item/1 y retornara la informacion de ese objeto en formato json
              
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
              get items
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <strong>Retorna una lista con todos los items que existen (Vista por defecto)</strong>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    


    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-A3rJD856KowSb7dwlZdYEkO39Gagi7vIsF0jrRAoQmDKKtQBHUuLZ9AsSv4jD4Xa" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/index.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
